snippet.title: NARROW ONE  - TRAILER - 🏹  Capture The Flag Medieval Style 🏹
snippet.description:
PLAY NARROW ONE HERE: https://narrow.one/
🏹 🏹 🏹
Battle players around the world with your bow and arrow. Defend your castle against invading foes. Steal the flag with the help of your teammates and win the battle. Narrow One is a multiplayer medieval-style bow and arrow shooter, 5v5. Explore the different maps and find the hidden shortcuts. Find cover and snipe other players from windows. Narrow One has touchscreen & gamepad support. 


Narrow One is developed by Pelican Party Studios.
